&lt;p&gt;Location: Claris Health Support Center, 1609 S. Barrington Ave., Los Angeles, CA&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours: Part-time, 20-29 hours/week&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reports to: Reality Check Program Manager&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
