&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Claris Health&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Claris Health, we’re more than just a healthcare organization—we’re a community dedicated to transforming lives. Our mission is to meet women and families right where they are, offering compassionate and practical support. As a community-based organization, we deeply believe in the work we do. We need a Reality Check Coordinator who shares that belief and can bring our mission to life by empowering the next generation through education.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you passionate about impacting the lives of youth? Do you thrive in dynamic environments where no two days are the same? We are seeking a dedicated and reliable &lt;strong&gt;Reality Check Coordinator&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this unique role, you&#39;ll combine your public speaking talents with your organizational skills to deliver our established curriculum to middle and high school students across a variety of educational settings, including public, Catholic, and Christian schools. You&#39;ll also handle administrative tasks like scheduling and coordinating with our team of speakers to ensure our program runs smoothly. Finally, you’ll contribute to Reality Check’s social media by helping create and post engaging educational content.&lt;/p&gt;
