&lt;p class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;Thank you for your interest in volunteering with Claris Health! Our volunteers are the heart of our organization, playing a crucial role in our ability to provide compassionate care and support to individuals and families in our community.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;We seek dedicated, reliable, and compassionate individuals who resonate with our core values and are committed to upholding our mission. Whether you can offer a few hours each week or contribute to specific projects, your involvement is deeply valued.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;Volunteering with Claris Health is a rewarding way to give back, gain experience, and connect with others who share your commitment to service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;strong class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;Ready to get involved?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
